## Svelte Guidelines

- Always write using Svelte 5 syntax using runes
- Snippets are used for creating components without declaring new component files.
- Snippets have syntax that looks like {#snippet}{/snippet} and contain DOM markup.
- Snippets do not go within the <script></script> block.